GET /2/users/:id/posts

// SociaVault: Same result
GET /v1/scrape/twitter/user-tweets?handle=elonmusk
```

```javascript
// X: Get user profile
GET /2/users/:id

// SociaVault: Same result
GET /v1/scrape/twitter/profile?handle=naval
```

```javascript
